## ğŸ›  Basic API

```ts
// Set a value
globalStore.set('player.hp', 10);

// Get a value
const hp = globalStore.get('player.hp');

// Check if a key exists
if (globalStore.has('player.hp')) { ... }

// Delete a key
globalStore.delete('player.hp');

// Reset entire store (e.g., from a save file)
